{"tid":58750,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"大局已定 - 沙田好運一月一","createTime":"2016-12-29T05:34:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-09T06:23:05.000Z","uid":52970,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5b1a3236ef1a0fa4e25920499e5f8438cf7658b6","tid":58750,"uid":52970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T05:34:38.000Z","msg":"拆解27號<br />\n賽前功課未做足，只俾左2串1，即場飛冇乜時間俾。<br />\nPost 返當日4隻<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmXbFMpbdnc8GoCQmc5LYgo4EeK324y2ZKJpzJqieXAXJK?filename=nX19Yv1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnX19Yv1.jpg&h=1205c1a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n拆解當日兩隻馬，綽綽有餘甘都輸都冇計，當日逆風太大，太初出頭，都會埋唔到尾，最後100力弱俾常妙星追過。有d輸當日場地，臨場有揀呢隻，買左小小試下<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/29/132435_e207398ad43280e92b982f46d29ba630.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F29%2F132435_e207398ad43280e92b982f46d29ba630.jpg&h=d6f820f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申先，當日未收錢前，每注一定係十蚊起機。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n加洲騰龍，臨場沙圈睇落到好，落到草地唔知做乜，好急(可以睇返當日行出草地既鏡頭)，已經有d折扣，不過最後都係做膽拖幾隻。豬左。 但會再跟進呢隻馬。<br />\n<br />\n當日臨場都有知多福，正是你，良才收到錢，小小斬獲。 <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/29/133354_b677bb33da76f77a3111c7269da1b1d0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F29%2F133354_b677bb33da76f77a3111c7269da1b1d0.jpg&h=d2f72c51&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmackRnjuMgz83HUgngTc8RLTPK8cnEj8BjiuX8qq6CWny?filename=gujo48N.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgujo48N.jpg&h=d2da2866&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家留力一月一<br />\n<br />\n有咩馬想傾下都可以。討論下"},{"pid":"8428d900baea34fc60b82c42f0e787f84e9ed496","tid":58750,"uid":52970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T07:36:56.000Z","msg":"有小小揀錯馬過關<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f98aa80465105e0a780dab3b494530d4798ff984","tid":58750,"uid":53404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T07:48:32.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"c89f227ac2c9eeade021573a202b5d97e92cdf8d","tid":58750,"uid":52283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T07:51:44.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"1b5a943248edf4d8e288300e8c37766d821e7c7f","tid":58750,"uid":22901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T08:28:09.000Z","msg":"樓主買馬主要睇咩？新手求教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0be6ad7e79ac0b76b3091a9dcfc4258a65ebab9f","tid":58750,"uid":52970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T08:41:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主買馬主要睇咩？新手求教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有人睇賠率，有人睇晨操，有人睇馬房操練，唔同派別都有，"},{"pid":"e44d2b90982f6c867b37695e7026d237a654abda","tid":58750,"uid":60807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T08:45:21.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7e62589977f114a250e7cfe44eecec3c37990bf","tid":58750,"uid":52970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T08:50:04.000Z","msg":"講下知多福個場，過關冇俾呢場，因為信心唔夠，<br />\n隻馬傷過，如果唔睇臨場狀態，豬左隨時。<br />\n<br />\n當然你買得冷，要預左博，但要有合理賠率，唔好豬左，就心灰，因為話明冷，就一定有風險。<br />\n<br />\n講返呢隻，到即場，辣辣椒大熱，呢d博格都贏唔到，最多俾個place你既，當然博爆冷。飛左佢，你揀熱門應該到春盈，飛又似。如果冷門，跑過既，冇野好博，得返知多福同仗義執言，仗義執言d閘冇個好睇，血統又係跑長，所以揀左知多福，拖幾隻舊馬。 都係博，但賭錢就係甘，熱門不穩當然求冷，春盈追唔切，條正q就爽。"},{"pid":"d7309f0f07953f5dc9ac22f5ad1babbbbd33612c","tid":58750,"uid":22901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T08:53:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓主買馬主要睇咩？新手求教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有人睇賠率，有人睇晨操，有人睇馬房操練，唔同派別都有，</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n之前係馬會個網撳過一次 有一頁列晒全部馬房有咩馬+頭馬etc 依家搵唔返，巴打知唔知點撳？求link<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9ac5c766a66c7b1723c7fe8fb0308b233dfce62","tid":58750,"uid":52970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T08:59:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>樓主買馬主要睇咩？新手求教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有人睇賠率，有人睇晨操，有人睇馬房操練，唔同派別都有，</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n之前係馬會個網撳過一次 有一頁列晒全部馬房有咩馬+頭馬etc 依家搵唔返，巴打知唔知點撳？求link<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n按練馬師資料？"},{"pid":"c51def90ace7f81c826dabdf8c0942f621c2de27","tid":58750,"uid":35661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T09:09:40.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"4379f9b501a120bbf82dc0542163c67b902ff3eb","tid":58750,"uid":29276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T09:13:17.000Z","msg":"黎名<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0c825e947936b3a42dd282479e3c4379be71db3","tid":58750,"uid":26672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T09:14:57.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"141b8bd803131d74ec63b6e179555e5784af6688","tid":58750,"uid":14964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T16:21:14.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a224c94dd5d40c34ee585afb952abe2051c1385","tid":58750,"uid":67942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T22:09:54.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"303adac533129a238dd36d635adbefc09929b244","tid":58750,"uid":25688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T19:40:06.000Z","msg":"蔡巴呢度仲出唔出水？"},{"pid":"a6004d644eb46313bbabd8e3ae9eeab63353401a","tid":58750,"uid":14964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T04:29:20.000Z","msg":"樓主呢？"},{"pid":"f178dcd094a33ffb92714d3b1637c64f9820c792","tid":58750,"uid":25688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T07:01:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主呢？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好可惜佢已經賣料唔出免費水<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cd64dc5979e6ba26dcd5acec81ace6df655225b","tid":58750,"uid":276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T08:10:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓主呢？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好可惜佢已經賣料唔出免費水<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實名巴如果唔係分身，相對正路啲"},{"pid":"170d066069ebf8893d1478e0581d312fa685ac07","tid":58750,"uid":276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-09T06:23:05.000Z","msg":"樓主，你大佬呢？有巴打話想報警，等緊隻傻狗覆，你合作開就通知一聲啦"}]}